commit.message:
Migrate to pdm-backend

Migrate from the deprecated pdm-pep517 backend to pdm-backend that
superseded it.  This required no changes to the project configuration
and generated equivalent artifacts.  The migration guide is at:
https://pdm-backend.fming.dev/migration/
